reviewText: Loved it! Good condition, rare for me to find and shipped on time :)I really enjoyed this part of ellen's story. I've heard about it and read about it, but this portrays it right in front of you.

Amazing!  I watch with bated breath, as the revelation of Ellen degeneres spilled over into my country,(England). I am so proud of Ellen and her family. This is a must see, for all Ellen fans and all so called Christains  as a guide! "How not behave when faced with homosexuality".
